Hukumomi sun ce wani kifi mai suna shark ya kai wa wani yaro ɗan shekara 13 hari kuma ya ji masa rauni sa'ad da yake shan ruwan 'yan damisa a ranar da ake buɗe lokacin kifin lobster a California.
