Yayin da ake jiran zabensa don cike gurbin wani alkalin kotun koli, Trump na neman karfafa goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar rasa rinjaye a majalisar dokoki a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi kamfen ɗin Trump a jihar West Virginia a yau kuma ta yaya za ka iya ganin sa a kan layi?
Trump zai fara taronsa a Wheeling, West Virginia da misalin karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon taron yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a yanar gizo ta hanyar YouTube ta hanyar dannawa a kasa.
Trump zai gabatar da kansa a wannan makon a gaban babban alkalin kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya shahara a kan zargin cin zarafin da aka yi masa, wanda ya jinkirta zaben tabbatar da shi a majalisar dattijai har tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken zargin.
Amma babban burin wannan jerin kamfen din shi ne tallafawa 'yan takarar Republican don samun nasara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar wani mai sharhi kan yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump, an ce, taron na makonni biyar masu zuwa, zai "taro masu son yin zabe da kuma masu goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican don karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Gudanar da majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga manufarsa, don haka shugaban yana shirye ya yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump da ba a bayyana sunansa ba.
A yau za a yi taron ne a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, kuma za a iya samun magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma 'yan jarida daga Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin wannan watan zuwa jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump ya goyi bayan dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican a majalisar dattijai na jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya samu koma baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Mr. Morris da shugaban ya yi kokarin kara masa goyon baya a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
