Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 kafin ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai na kan gaba a wasan Ryder Cup bayan da ta ci Amurka 10-6 a wasan hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Kyakkyawan ma'aurata Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci tseren nasara da biyu daga Tiger Woods mai ban mamaki, kuma sun sami maki huɗu a yau a Le Golf National.
Thomas Bjorn, dan wasan Turai, wanda ya yi kokarin da ya kamata ya ci nasara a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya yi nasara a kan Amurka a wasan da suka yi a safiyar yau, inda suka ci wasan 3-1.
Amurka ta fi kowa ƙarfi a wasanni huɗu, ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage ragamar ba.
Jim Fury ya bukaci maki takwas daga cikin wasanni 12 da suka buga a ranar Lahadi domin ya ci.
Fleetwood ita ce ta farko da ta fara buga gasar Turai da ta ci kwallaye hudu a jere. ita da Molinari, wanda ake kira Molliwood, sun zama biyu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da suka ci kwallaye hudu a wasanni hudu na farko.
Bayan sun fara murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kwando, sai suka kara da karfi wajen kammala wasan da Woods da Bryson Dechambeau suka yi da suka yi kasa da karfinta, 5-4.
Woods, wanda ya yi fama da rashin nasara a wasannin biyu da ya buga a ranar Asabar, ya yi fice a wasu lokatai, amma ya sha kashi 19 cikin 29 a wasansa na hudu da hudu, har ma da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose ya huta daga wasannin kwallon kafa na safe, amma ya sake komawa wasan hudu tare da Henrik Stenson, amma ya rasa 2-1 ga Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, wadanda ke kan gaba da na uku a jerin.
Turai ba ta samu duk abin da take so ba a wannan rana mai kyau da ta dace daga Paris zuwa kudu maso yamma.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, 'yan wasan da suka lashe gasar zakarun Turai sau uku, sun ci gaba da yin nasara a gasar zakarun Amurka da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2-1 a kan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan kwata-kwata, kuma daga baya suka ci 4-3 a kan Poulter da Rory McIlroy a wasan kwata-kwata, duk da haka sun rasa ramukan farko biyu.
A cikin tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, sau biyu ne kawai aka samu wani rukuni da ya tashi daga matsayi na hudu zuwa matsayi a lokacin da aka fara wasan biyu, ko da yake Fury ya ci nasara.
Ko da yake, bayan kwana biyu na zama na biyu mafi kyau, wataƙila an nemi ƙarin lokaci don yin faɗa a ranar Lahadi.
Koriya ta Arewa ba za ta taba yin watsi da makaman ta ba idan ba ta amince da juna ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa, tsauraran takunkumi da ake yi wa kasar sun kara janyo rashin amincewa da Amurka ne kawai, kuma a wannan yanayi babu wata dama da Koriya ta Arewa za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta baki daya.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki 'matakan alheri' a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na makami mai linzami, rushe wurin gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma alkawarin da ta yi cewa ba za ta kara yawan makaman nukiliya ko fasahar ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga irin wannan aikin daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za mu iya tabbatar da tsaron kasa ba, don haka a irin wannan yanayi, ba za mu iya kawar da makamanmu ba.
Ko da yake Ri ya sake maimaita sanannen korafin da ake yi cewa Washington ba za ta amince da matakin da za ta dauka na kawar da makaman nukiliya ba, inda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada a kowane mataki, amma abin da ya ce yana da muhimmanci domin ba a kawar da makaman nukiliya baki daya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya ambaci sanarwar hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka bayar a taron farko na shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi kokarin kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950 zuwa 1953, amma Amurka ta bukaci Pyongyang ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliyarta.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi hamayya da sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da aka sanya wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta bukaci a kawar da makaman nukiliya da farko, kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar amfani da karfi  har ma da adawa da yardar zaman lafiya , in ji Ri.
Tunanin cewa takunkumi zai sa mu durƙusa shi ne burin masu son yin wasa.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da takunkumi yana ƙara sa mu ƙara rashin amincewa da juna.
Ri bai ambaci shirin gudanar da taron koli na Kim da Trump ba, amma Trump da kansa ya bayyana hakan a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya jaddada ganawarsa da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in sau uku a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: Idan Koriya ta Kudu ce ta bukaci a kwance makamai maimakon Amurka, da ba za a samu irin wannan matsalar ba.
Amma sautin muryar Rin ya sha bamban da na bara, lokacin da ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba za a iya kaucewa harin Amurka ba bayan da Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "mai harin kunar bakin wake".
A bara, Trump ya yi barazanar 'halaka' Koriya ta Arewa, amma a wannan shekarar, Trump ya yaba wa Kim sosai kan yadda ya yi kokarin kawar da makamansa, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da iyaka: "Idan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, ko uku ko watanni biyar, ba kome".
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta amince da Pyongyang kan ci gaban da ta samu.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa Ƙarfafa takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro dole ne ya ci gaba da ƙarfi kuma ba tare da gazawa ba har sai mun tabbatar da cikakken, ƙarshe da kuma tabbatar da watsi da makaman nukiliya.
Tun daga shekarar 2006, Kwamitin Tsaro ya tsaurara takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa da nufin dakile hanyoyin samar da makaman nukiliya da na ballistic daga Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Koriya ta Arewa a lokacin taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, kuma ya sanar da cewa zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar da ya yi a baya ba ta tafi daidai ba.
Da ya bar birnin Pyongyang, ya bayyana cewa an samu ci gaba, amma Koriya ta Arewa ta yi tir da bukatar da Pompeo ya yi na 'yan daba'i' bayan sa'o'i kadan.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rufe sansanin makaman nukiliya da tashar nukiliya a ganawar da ta yi da Sakatare Janar Moon a farkon wannan watan idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
A cewar Pompeo, Kim yana nufin "da matakan da suka dace" da tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a ganawar da ya yi da Singapore da kuma matsawa zuwa daidaita dangantakar da ke tsakanin kasar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna yin darasi game da samun isashen hutu
A wannan shekara, dukan ɗaliban da ke karatun digiri na biyu a Jami'ar Harvard za su halarci wani darasi da aka tsara don ƙara yawan hutu a ɗaliban, wanda zai zama abin ƙyama ga al'adun maza da ke ci gaba a jami'ar, inda ɗalibai ke yin barci da dare a kan maganin kafeyin.
Wani mai bincike ya ce ɗaliban da ke makarantar jami'a mafi kyau a duniya ba su san kome game da abubuwan da za su taimaka musu su kasance da koshin lafiya ba.
Farfesa Charles Czeisler, wanda yake aiki a asibitin Brigham and Women's Hospital a Harvard Medical School, wanda ya tsara wannan darasi ya gaskata cewa wannan darasi ne na farko a Amirka.
Czeisler ya sami wannan ra'ayin ne bayan ya ba da jawabi game da yadda rashin barci yake shafar koyo.
Bayan darasin, wata matashiya ta zo wurina kuma ta ce, "Me ya sa ban san wannan ba sai yanzu, a shekarata ta ƙarshe a makaranta?"
Babu wanda ya taba gaya mata game da bukatar barci, wanda na yi mamakin shi, in ji ta a wata hira da Telegraph.
A karon farko a wannan shekara, an shirya wani darasi da zai koya wa ɗalibai yadda yin barci da kyau zai taimaka musu su yi nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni.
Farfesa Paul Barreira, wanda shi ne mataimakin shugaban kula da lafiyar jami'ar Harvard Medical School, ya ce jami'ar ta daina koyar da darasin ne bayan ta ji cewa ɗalibai suna rashin barci sosai a lokacin makaranta.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani sashe, ana nuna wa ɗalibai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibi zai iya danna kofi, labule, kayan wasanni, da littattafai don ya sami bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci yake shafan wasanni da kuma muhimmancin yin ayyuka na dare.
A wani sashe kuma, za a koya wa masu sauraro yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya sa su kamu da ciwon zuciya, shanyewar jiki, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar da ke dauke da hotuna masu amfani da juna, za ta sa masu halartar taron su yi tunani a kan al'adarsu ta yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa wannan ba zai shafi halin ɗaliban nan da nan ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin sanin waɗannan abubuwa kamar yadda suke da hakkin sanin sakamakon shan taba a kan lafiyarsu", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ce, nazarin dare-dare har ila abin alfahari ne, kuma fasaha da matsi da ɗalibai suke fuskanta suna sa rashin barci ya zama matsala.
"Samun isasshen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama makamin  na ɗalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, har ma da yin kiba, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta zama kamar mai yunwa, kuma hakan yana sa mutum ya ci gaba da jin yunwa", in ji Farfesa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan shekara 19 a California, ɗalibin ilimin halayyar mutum da na sinadarai, ya taimaki Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussan da yake koyarwa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard a bara.
Ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya motsa shi ya yi wani darasi da zai shafi dukan ɗaliban makarantar.
Ya yi fatan cewa duk daliban da ke karatun digiri na biyu za su iya kammala irin wannan karatun kafin su koma wata cibiyar da ke da gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ce idan ɗalibai suka kafa ƙararrawa, za su tuna da lokacin da za su yi barci da kuma lokacin da za su farka da safe.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: harbin Menga ya ci nasara a hannun 'yan wasan Gerrard
Steven Gerrard da Rangers sun sake fuskantar wata ranar rashin nasara yayin da harbi da Dolly Menga ta yi ta hanyar tsaron da ya fashe ya ba Livingston nasara 1-0.
'Yan wasan Ibrox sun nemi nasarar su ta farko tun wasan 41 da suka buga a watan Fabrairu da suka gabata da St. Johnstone. Amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta yi nasara a wannan karon, kuma Gerrard ya sha wahala ne kawai a karo na biyu a cikin wasannin 18 da ya yi a matsayin manajan. Rangers ta yi kasa da maki takwas a kan Hearts.
Menga ya buga kwallo a raga da minti bakwai kafin rabi, kuma rashin karfin gwiwar Rangers bai daidaita lamarin ba.
A sakamakon haka, Rangers sun koma matsayi na shida, amma Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku, wanda kawai Hibernian ke da shi a raga.
'Yan wasan Rangers na iya fuskantar wasu matsaloli, kamar yadda Calum Spence ya ji rauni a kan kai lokacin da aka jefa shi daga gidan wasan waje, kuma an yi masa magani.
Gerrard ya yi sau takwas a cikin tawagar da ta doke Ayr kuma ta ci gaba zuwa wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Ingila.
Holt ya ci gaba da zama a cikin tawagar Livi 11 da suka ci Hearts a makon da ya gabata, kuma wannan dabarar ta sake haifar da sakamako, tare da kyakkyawan tsari wanda ya ci gaba da azabtar da abokan hamayyarsa a kusan kowane juyi.
Duk da cewa Rangers sun yi nasara wajen mamaye filin, Livingston ya fi amfani da yanayin don amfanin kansa.
Livingston ya samu damar zura kwallo a raga a minti biyu da fara wasan Menga, inda Scott Pittman ya samu damar zura kwallo a raga ta Allan McGregor, amma Pittman bai yi nasarar zura kwallo ba.
Keaghan Jacobs ya tura wa Craig Halket kwallo ta baya, amma dan wasan baya Alan Lithgow ya samu damar buga kwallo a baya.
A wani bangare kuma, Rangers sun samu nasarar jan ragamar wasan, amma a ƙarshen wasan, babu wani tabbaci a cikin iska.
Alfredo Morelos ya nemi a hukunta shi bayan da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless a minti na 15 amma Alkalin wasa Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da bukatar ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun samu nasarar zura kwallo biyu a raga a farkon rabin wasan, amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox Liam Kelly ya yi nasarar kawar da kwallo biyu daga Lassana Coulibaly da kuma Ovie Ejari.
Livingston ya ci kwallo a minti na 34 kuma hakan ya sa ya yi mamaki sosai, amma hakan ba don ƙwazo da 'yan wasan suka yi ba ne kawai.
Har ila yau, Rangers ba su iya yin wani abu game da yadda Jacobs ya yi amfani da dogon lokaci ba.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba Scott Robinson, wanda ya ba da ball a cikin sanyi don Mengu ya ci shi.
A cikin canji, Gerrard ya yanke shawarar maye gurbin Coulibaly kuma ya sanya Ryan Kent a filin wasa. Canjin ya shafi wasan kusan nan take lokacin da Kent ya samar da rami mai kyau ga Morelos.
Livingston ya sake sanya baƙi su sake buga wasan nasu yayin da Lithgow da Halkett suka ci gaba da yin dogon wasa a jere.
Holt da 'yan wasansa sun samu damar karawa juna karfi a wasan amma McGregor ya yi amfani da karfinsa wajen karewa, wanda ya kawo karshen kokarin da Jacobs ke yi kafin Lithgow ya kai ga inda yake a kusurwa.
Glenn Middleton, wanda aka yi musayarsa daga Rangers, ya nemi a ba shi bugun bugun daga hannun Jacobs, amma kuma Thomson ya juya baya.
