Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi a duniya ya shirya kaddamar da sabuwar yanar gizo a matsayin wani hari kan Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani mai farawa da nufin yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin da aka yi a baya-bayan nan na wannan sanannen masanin fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke da tushen tushen tushen Berners-Lee mai suna Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawarar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar kowane bayanai.
A wata hira da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi ba'a cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
Ya kamata a yi shi yanzu, in ji ta game da kamfani na farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Wannan app yana amfani da fasahar Solid don mutane su iya ƙirƙirar nasu taro na sirri ko POD.
Zai iya haɗa da jerin sunayen lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan tunawa, kalanda, laburaren kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna aiki a cikin burauzar guda a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa bayanan sirri na sirri ya bambanta shi ne, yana da cikakken iko a kan mai amfani wanda zai iya samun dama ga irin bayanan da yake da su.
Kamfanin ya kira shi haɓaka mutum ta hanyar bayanai.
A cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewar da ake buƙata don samar da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, tsarin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi hayar su don aiki tare da aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu aikin sa kai.
Masu fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa tattaunawa da Facebook da Google kan ko za su ba mutane sauyi na gaba daya wanda zai juya tsarin kasuwancin su gaba daya cikin dare guda.
Ba ma tambayar su ko sun yarda da hakan.
A cikin wani labarin da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt aikinta ne ta samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don haɗin kai da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina a Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a Intanet ta hanyar kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa a matsayin wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban kungiyar World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute bayan fara Inrupt.
Ina da matuƙar kwarin gwiwa game da sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo Berners-Lee ya kara da cewa.
