An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
An shirya sabuwar jirgin ruwan sojin ruwan Jamus da za a fara aiki a shekarar 2014, jirgin na nufin maye gurbin kayan aikin Cold War da ke tsufa, amma za a fara aiki a farkon shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar farashi, in ji kafofin yada labarai na kasar.
A cewar wani jami'in soji da ya yi magana da jaridar Die Zeit, an dage shigar da jirgin ruwa na farko na sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya jirgin zai shiga cikin rundunar jiragen ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da ke tattare da samar da kayayyaki sun hana wannan shiri.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Württemberg da aka ba da umarni a 2007 suna nufin maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bayanai da ke akwai sun nuna cewa za a sanye su da manyan bindigogi, da na'urorin harba makamai masu linzami da na sama da na sama, da kuma fasahar ɓoyewa, kamar su radar, da kuma fasahar rage hasken infrared da sauti.
Wani muhimmin fasali na jirgin shine tsawon lokacin da yake aiki  sabbin jiragen ruwa zasu iya aiki a teku har tsawon shekaru biyu ba tare da zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa ba.
Amma, ci gaba da jinkirin da ake yi yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa masu ƙwarewa  da ake ce suna da nufin ƙarfafa ikon Jamus a ƙasashen waje  sun riga sun zama tsofaffi a lokacin da suka soma aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
An yi ta buga labarai a shekarar da ta gabata bayan da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ki amincewa da jirgin da aka yi amfani da shi, kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta dawo da jirgin bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da shi ba, amma kafofin yada labaran Jamus sun yi magana game da manyan "kurakurai a cikin software da kayan aiki" wanda ya sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani ga ayyukan yaƙi.
Rashin software yana da mahimmanci saboda yawan ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg yana da kimanin 120, wanda shine kawai rabin rabin tsofaffin 'yan fashin jirgin ruwa na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya rage damar da jirgin zai iya samun sabuntawa.
An ce Rhineland-Palatinate mai tan 7,000 tana da nauyin fiye da na jiragen ruwa iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da rashin ingancin kayan aiki, farashin aikin yana ci gaba da zama matsala.
An ƙaru farashin zuwa dala biliyan 3.1 daga asalin farashin biliyan 2.2.
Matsalar shigar da sababbin jiragen ruwa ya bayyana bayan da aka yi gargaɗi kwanan nan cewa sojojin Jamus za su ragu.
Shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus Hans-Peter Bartels ya ce a farkon wannan shekarar jiragen ruwa masu amfani da jiragen ruwa na 'ƙarancin' su.
Hukumar ta ce matsalar ta ƙaru ne a tsawon lokaci domin an daina amfani da tsofaffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a yi amfani da sababbin jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wata jirgi mai suna Baden-Württemberg da aka ba da damar shiga cikin jirgin ruwa.
