Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawes ne, wanda ke bakin wani bakin teku mai nisan kilomita biyu a yammacin tsibirin Sulawes, kuma a shekarar 2017 yawan jama'arsa ya kai 379,800.
An yi wata girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a tsakiyar bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwar birnin.
Gundumar Donggala ta kai kilomita 300 (180 miles) daga gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawes.
A cikin shekarar 2017, an kiyasta yawan mutanen da ke zaune a garin Donggala su kai 299,200.
Babban aikin tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawes, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku, shine kamun kifi da noma.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da muhimmanci, amma yana da yawa a Morowal, a gabar tekun Sulawes.
