Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin Tekun Fasifik kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi muni a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a arewacin Sumatra da ke yammacin lardin Aceh a ƙasar Indonesia ta haddasa tsunami da ya addabi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gaɓar tekun Indiya.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin tsibirin Java, babban tsibirin ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a gaɓar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai a Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 30 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, ta haddasa bala'i da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da mummunar lalacewar da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a 2004.
Amma a wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-ginen suka rushe.
